  <title xml:lang="EN">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Ensuring human rights of convicted criminals with the revision of the law on enforcement of criminal judgements</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1" xml:lang="EN">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project aims at influencing the law-making process in order to better ensure rights of convicted criminals under the Constitution of Vietnam. The projects specially focuses on the Law On Amending a Number of Articles of The Law on Enforcement of Criminal Judgements. This Law greatly relates to life of millions of custodial as well as non-custodial convicted criminals as it regulates their rights and obligations while serving criminal judgements.</narrative>
  </description>
